title: Add BattleNotFoundEvent when empty field received
message:
Add BattleNotFoundEvent when empty field received

When re-connect is done (v1.1.0+), the server sends to us restored
state and everything starts to work again. But what if the battle
has just been finished? Then the server sends an empty field, and
the client "hungs up"; so here is a fix

title: Rename 2 Dialogs (ONLY)

1) DialogFinished -> DialogFinishedEx
2) DialogFinishedSimple -> DialogFinished

title: Add a new nifty dialog to Training Screen
message:

Earlier I reuse the same dialog for both Screens (Battle and Training)
so that a dialog in Training Screen looked very empty; now I created
individual dialogs for each of them

title: Add extra protection: MOVE allowed after reconnect
message:
Add extra protection: MOVE allowed after reconnect

In v. 1.1.1. I added a check: while we have not received MoveAck we
are not allowed to send the next MOVE cmd;
But what to do in case of lost and recover connection? So this patch
fixes this occasion

title: Add hot fix: hangup in Training
message:
Add hot fix: hangup in Training

In v1.1.1 I added waiting for MOVE Ack for BattleScreen, but I forget
about TrainingScreen; so this is patch for it

title: Fix excessive sending of MOVE when poor connection
message:
Fix excessive sending of MOVE when poor connection

When we've got poor internet-connection, a user may tap on the
right of a screen to make a character move and discover that
a character is boggled. So in this patch we forbind sending next
MOVE cmd until we receive Ack on previous one from the Server
